  "detailed_description": "■New version<br>3.1<br>A new toilet race with many new features!<br><br><strong>Let's start Toilet Race!!</strong><br>Benza Race, where the world's toilet racers compete to get the title of \"The Toilet\", is finally revealed.<br>Play on your PC and you will fully enjoy this Benza Race!<br><br><strong>Paper Shot and killer technics:</strong><br>Benza Racers have paper shots and killer technics by characters.<br>These technics can give you advantages on races. <br>However, the shots are limited, so you need to catch Onigiri (riceballs) on the street to charge the shots power.<br>Burst your shots at the critical timing!<br><br><strong>Depict world wide courses:</strong><br>You can enjoy the race courses such as the famous Toto Town, Hescatore Stadium, and Ben Joe Street!<br>These various courses have different characteristics, and you will see blocks, dogs, traps which makes racers trapped down!<br>Go over these hardships and be the revolutionary Hunbalt!",
  "about_the_game": "■New version<br>3.1<br>A new toilet race with many new features!<br><br><strong>Let's start Toilet Race!!</strong><br>Benza Race, where the world's toilet racers compete to get the title of \"The Toilet\", is finally revealed.<br>Play on your PC and you will fully enjoy this Benza Race!<br><br><strong>Paper Shot and killer technics:</strong><br>Benza Racers have paper shots and killer technics by characters.<br>These technics can give you advantages on races. <br>However, the shots are limited, so you need to catch Onigiri (riceballs) on the street to charge the shots power.<br>Burst your shots at the critical timing!<br><br><strong>Depict world wide courses:</strong><br>You can enjoy the race courses such as the famous Toto Town, Hescatore Stadium, and Ben Joe Street!<br>These various courses have different characteristics, and you will see blocks, dogs, traps which makes racers trapped down!<br>Go over these hardships and be the revolutionary Hunbalt!",
